name: lulu in wonderland (8)
description:
continue to story lulu in wonderland (8).
Finally Lulu can pass through this land of vegetables, even though evil is sacrificed and has to eat vegetables. Lulu sees a unique sword stuck in Pak Tomato's plantation, Pak Tomato warns Lulu, the sword can never be pulled out. it is said that the sword exists because seeds from heaven come down from the sky
